# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TravelPro (YOMKEF) — Environment Variables
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# Convex env vars go in the Convex dashboard, not here.

# ─── Convex (required for local dev) ───
CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT=dev:your-deployment-slug
VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://your-deployment-slug.convex.cloud
VITE_CONVEX_SITE_URL=https://your-deployment-slug.convex.site

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MVP — Set these in the Convex dashboard env vars
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── AI (OpenRouter → Gemini Flash) ───
# Used for: marketing descriptions, trip name generation,
# image cleanup, invoice analysis, AI onboarding
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# ─── WhatsApp Business API ───
# Primary notification channel (Israel preference)
# Used for: availability requests, time-shift updates,
# quantity notifications, booking confirmations, reminders
# Options: Twilio WhatsApp, 360dialog, or Meta Cloud API
WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=
WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=

# ─── SMS (Twilio) ───
# Fallback when WhatsApp is unavailable
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=

# ─── Email (Resend) ───
# Tertiary notification channel + document expiry alerts
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...

# ─── Payment System ───
# Decision pending (Polar vs Cardcom vs other) — discuss with Eran
# Uncomment the one you choose:
# POLAR_API_KEY=
# CARDCOM_TERMINAL_NUMBER=
# CARDCOM_API_NAME=
# CARDCOM_API_PASSWORD=

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# POST-MVP — Not needed until after launch (PRD §10)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Canva API (Save the Date image generation) ───
# CANVA_API_KEY=

# ─── ManyChat (B2C lead capture from gallery) ───
# MANYCHAT_API_KEY=

# ─── Google Business API (pull supplier ratings) ───
# GOOGLE_BUSINESS_API_KEY=

# ─── External Storage (heavy media — gallery photos/videos) ───
# Consider Cloudflare R2 or AWS S3 if Convex storage costs too much
# CLOUDFLARE_R2_ACCESS_KEY=
# CLOUDFLARE_R2_SECRET_KEY=
# CLOUDFLARE_R2_BUCKET=
# CLOUDFLARE_R2_ENDPOINT=
